text: Johnsson is a Swedish surname meaning "son of John". People with this surname include: * Christofer Johnsson, Swedish heavy metal musician * Kim Johnsson, Swedish ice hockey player * Sonja Johnsson, Swedish Swimmer * William G. Johnsson, former editor of the Adventist Review == See also == * Jonson * Jonsson * Johanson * Johansson Category:Swedish-language surnames Category:Patronymic surnames
title: Johnsson
